description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment to provide new buildings ranging between five and seven storeys in height to provide 117 residential units (51 one-bedroom flats, 29 two-bedroom flats, 27 three-bedroom flats and 10 four-bedroom flats) including balconies and roof terraces, 2263 sqm of use-class B1 floorspace, 145 sqm of use-class A3 floorspace and associated parking, cycle storage and landscaping. (REVISED DESCRIPTION, including submission of additional information for materials and landscape proposals).
